oub:certificate.description.oub:description: Certificate of origin Form A bearing the endorsement "Derogation — Commission Implementing Regulation (EU) No 2018/348"

oub:quota.definition.oub:description: COMMISSION IMPLEMENTING REGULATION (EU) 2018/348 of 8 March 2018 on a temporary derogation from the rules of preferential origin laid down in Delegated Regulation (EU) 2015/2446 in respect of bicycles and other cycles produced in Cambodia regarding the use, under cumulation, of parts originating in Malaysia (OJ L 67, p.24)

oub:footnote.description.oub:description: Eligibility to benefit from this tariff quota is subject to the production of a certificate of origin Form A with the following entered in box 4 "Derogation — Commission Implementing Regulation (EU) No 2018/348" in accordance with the conditions laid down in Regulation (EU) No 2018/348 (OJ L 67).

oub:quota.definition.oub:description: Council Regulation (EU) 2016/2389 amending Regulation (EU) No 1388/2013 opening and providing for the management of autonomous tariff quotas of the Union for certain agricultural and industrial products (OJ L 360, 30/12/2016)
